{"tid":569411,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊回顧下李居明條神棍點吹水","createTime":"2018-02-22T16:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T20:06:34.000Z","uid":40525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a5cf87e213d03256c9e989e4786f39e5f19d2e","tid":569411,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"原link: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sQ2Qj0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sQ2Qj0&d=ZRIXzU2NY6P31ttKCpkdv8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=53639147\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sQ2Qj0</a><br />\n<br />\n事件：<br />\n1.李居明係訪問老吹話「龍貓」個名係自己作<br />\nlink: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sQ2Qj0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sQ2Qj0&d=ZRIXzU2NY6P31ttKCpkdv8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=53639147\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sQ2Qj0</a><br />\n／／1986年《天空之城》 在香港掀起宮崎駿之風。宮崎駿不負眾望，《となりのトトロ》再次成為動畫經典。日本片商在1988年正計劃輸入香港，那隻大田鼠有一個可愛的日文名叫「トトロ(Totoro)」。在日本是「トトロ」就是「トトロ」，但來到香港實在考起電影宣傳，電影公司向李居明請教。<br />\n<br />\n「トトロ本身是一隻田鼠，但香港人會覺得鼠係唔吉利，咁不如叫做貓啦。」就這樣，成為了今日耳熟能詳的「龍貓」。李居明還將兩隻配角小田鼠改作「吱吱喳」「Bom Bom Ba」猜枚的名字，「兩隻嘢行路發出聲音『吱吱喳』『Bom Bom Ba』，笑到啲細路仔不得了。」一隻「龍貓」，改變了李居明的靈界路線。原來改名起題，比今日在社交媒體落Tag，更可以點石成金，一下子令李居明成為炙手可熱的電影宣傳人，他開始為日本動畫監督配音。／／<br />\n<br />\n2.有當年漫週嘅同事踢爆，天地有正氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/001939_14deac65594cefb3524ea8fc0c10d754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F001939_14deac65594cefb3524ea8fc0c10d754.jpg&h=1d0e5005&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e8a97588f6229b53dae0e928b0b241959695f87","tid":569411,"uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/002327_b362d7d1035e7e3a796a653d152f1fcf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F002327_b362d7d1035e7e3a796a653d152f1fcf.png&h=5ffee934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林子善"},{"pid":"0260f38ad1de10a591b69b8c54f39d209dfd15fd","tid":569411,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924700d57b97217c1e3f8ed116fad09b088287cc","tid":569411,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:30:47.000Z","msg":"pish!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d841add0fa42d1ceec53076575ddedf1a9476dab","tid":569411,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T19:55:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/娛樂/162164/李居明自稱-龍貓-命名人-前漫畫周刊員工爆-我哋一定最先最快\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F162164%2F%E6%9D%8E%E5%B1%85%E6%98%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1-%E9%BE%8D%E8%B2%93-%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA-%E5%89%8D%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%91%A8%E5%88%8A%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%88%86-%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%80%E5%85%88%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB&d=ZRIXzU2NY6P31ttKCpkdv8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2237edbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/娛樂/162164/李居明自稱-龍貓-命名人-前漫畫周刊員工爆-我哋一定最先最快</a>"},{"pid":"352c5f853598c30d63e5021e3160b2677892e154","tid":569411,"uid":35296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T20:06:34.000Z","msg":"LM待恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}